title: AKCP: Drycontact Sensor
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/akcp
license: GPL
distribution:
description:
 This check monitors the status of a AKCP Drycontact Sensor.

 The states

 - "no status"

 - "sensor error"

 - "output low"

 - "output high"

 go {CRIT} by default. The result of these states can be configured.

 All other states are defined in MIB.

 The check uses the SPAGENT-MIB.

item:
 The description of the sensor as string as specified by the user during board configuration.

inventory:
 One service is created for each sensor if the sensor is online.

